df_precip = df.copy()

# Create the 'y' column
df_precip['y'] = df_precip['Precip Type'].replace(['rain', 'snow'], [1, 0])

# Drop any rows with missing values
df_precip_dropped = df_precip.dropna(subset=['y'])

# Convert the 'Year' column to datetime format
df_precip_dropped['ds'] = pd.to_datetime(df_precip_dropped['Year'])

# Drop duplicates in the 'ds' column
df_precip_dropped.drop_duplicates(subset=['ds'], inplace=True)

# Create the NeuralProphet model
model = NeuralProphet(epochs=500)

# Fit the model to the data
model.fit(df_precip_dropped[['ds','y']], freq='D')
